m tracking-[-0.01em]\">Aprovação</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Vês tudo antes de sair e ajustamos o que quiseres — sem surpresas.</p><p class=\"mt-2.5 flex items-baseline gap-2\"><span class=\"font-heading text-xl font-medium text-accent leading-none\">0</span><span class=\"text-[12px] text-muted\">surpresas — aprovas tudo</span></p></li></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><li class=\"relative pl-12\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute left-[6px] top-1 grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full border border-accent/50 bg-bg\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span></span><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent\">Passo <!-- -->5</p><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-xl font-medium tracking-[-0.01em]\">Publicação &amp; relatório</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Publico ou agendo e mostro-te, com simplicidade, o que funcionou melhor.</p><p class=\"mt-2.5 flex items-baseline gap-2\"><span class=\"font-heading text-xl font-medium text-accent leading-none\">Mensal</span><span class=\"text-[12px] text-muted\">relatório simples</span></p></li></div></ol></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24\" aria-labelledby=\"resultados\"><div class=\"max-w-[1080px] mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-[640px] mx-auto mb-14\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4\">O que muda</p><h2 id=\"resultados\" class=\"text-white\">Presença que trabalha por ti</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed\">Sem promessas de viral. O que entrego é constância, imagem profissional e o teu tempo livre.</p></div><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center mb-6\"><p class=\"flex-1 text-center text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-dark\">Antes</p><span 