><path d=\"M0 50 C 45 50, 55 50, 100 50\" stroke=\"rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16)\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" vector-effect=\"non-scaling-stroke\"></path><path d=\"M0 50 C 45 50, 55 50, 100 50\" pathLength=\"100\" stroke=\"var(--accent)\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-opacity=\"1\" vector-effect=\"non-scaling-stroke\" class=\"flow-dots\" style=\"animation-delay:1.4s\"></path></g><g><path d=\"M0 50 C 45 50, 55 84, 100 84\" stroke=\"rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16)\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" vector-effect=\"non-scaling-stroke\"></path><path d=\"M0 50 C 45 50, 55 84, 100 84\" pathLength=\"100\" stroke=\"var(--accent)\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-opacity=\"1\" vector-effect=\"non-scaling-stroke\" class=\"flow-dots\" style=\"animation-delay:1.9s\"></path></g></svg></div><div class=\"md:hidden flex justify-center h-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 0 3px rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.85))\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 100\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" fill=\"none\" class=\"h-full w-5\"><path d=\"M10 0 L10 100\" stroke=\"rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16)\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" vector-effect=\"non-scaling-stroke\"></path><path d=\"M10 0 L10 100\" pathLength=\"100\" stroke=\"var(--accent)\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-opacity=\"1\" vector-effect=\"non-scaling-stroke\" class=\"flow-dots\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"md:flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 lg:gap-7\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-accent/25 bg-accent/[0.06] p-4 lg:p-5 text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-heading text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">Sempre</div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-accent\">Ativo e consistente</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-accent/25 bg-accent/[0.06] p-4 lg:p-5 text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-heading text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">~0h</div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-accent\">do teu tempo · tu aprovas</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-accent/25 bg-accent/[0.06] p-4 lg:p-5 text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-heading text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">100%</div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-accent\">à imagem da tua marca</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"preco\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-14\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4\">Investimento</p><h2 id=\"preco\" class=\"text-white\">Preços claros, sem surpresas</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Avença mensal para presença contínua, ou packs pontuais quando precisares de um empurrão.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-white/10 bg-[#0c0d10] p-3 sm:p-4 md:p-5\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_minmax(0,440px)] gap-3 sm:gap-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[22px] bg-bg-card/40 p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-dark mb-7\">Incluído em todos os pacotes</p><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-7\"><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M21 11.5a8 8 0 0 1-11.5 7.2L4 20l1.3-5.4A8 8 0 1 1 21 11.5Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Gestão de redes</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Trato das tuas redes com conteúdo planeado e publicado — presença sem te ocupar.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" rx=\"2\"></rect><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"m21 15-5-5L5 21\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Conteúdo &amp; design</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Posts com design profissional e copy que para o scroll — com a tua identidade.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"m10 9 5 3-5 3V9Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Vídeo vertical</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Reels, TikToks e Shorts com legendas, hook e CTA — o formato que mais alcança hoje.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"4\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Calendário de conteúdo</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Um plano mensal claro: sabes o que sai e quando. Nada de improviso.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M4 4h16v12H7l-3 3V4Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Copy que gera ação</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Legendas pensadas para interação e para levar à ação — não só para somar likes.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3.5\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] text-accent\"><svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"></circle><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 2\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-tight\">Sem te roubar tempo</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-muted text-[13px] leading-snug\">Tu aprovas, eu trato do resto. As redes ativas sem ocupar a tua agenda.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-auto pt-8\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-2\"><span class=\"flex gap-0.5 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.9 6.3L22 9.3l-5 4.6 1.3 6.8L12 17.5 5.7 20.7 7 13.9l-5-4.6 7.1-1z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[12px] text-white/80\"><span class=\"text-white font-medium\">5,0</span> no Google · 7 avaliações</span></div></div></div><div class=\"relative rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#191d24] via-[#121419] to-[#0c0d10] p-6 sm:p-7 shadow-[0_30px_70px_-30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.9)] overflow-hidden\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -top-20 -right-16 w-60 h-60 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 60% 40%, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16), transparent 65%)\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-6 min-h-[28px]\"><span class=\"rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-accent font-medium\">Mais escolhido</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-muted\">por mês · recorrente</span></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-heading text-2xl font-medium tracking-[-0.01em]\">Gestão de Social Media</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed min-h-[40px]\">Criação e gestão de conteúdo com escopo definido (volume controlado).</p><div class=\"mt-5\"><span class=\"text-white font-heading text-[40px] leading-none font-medium tracking-[-0.02em]\">197€</span></div><ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>Conteúdo planeado e publicado</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>Design + copy com a tua identidade</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>Calendário mensal de conteúdo</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/85\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 mt-px rounded-full bg-accent/15 text-accent\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span>Relatório simples todos os meses</li></ul></div><div class=\"mt-7\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-dark mb-3\">Escolhe o pacote</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"true\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-accent/50 bg-accent/15 text-white\">Gestão de Social Media</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/25\">Pack de Posts</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"rounded-full border px-3.5 py-2 sm:py-1.5 text-[12px] font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/25\">Pack Vídeo Vertical</button></div></div><div class=\"mt-7\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body w-full\" href=\"/contacto?servico=Social%20Media\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Pedir orçamento grátis</span></a></div><p class=\"mt-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-muted\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-accent\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>Orçamento e diagnóstico gratuitos</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"faq\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Em que redes trabalham?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Instagram, Facebook e TikTok — conforme onde estão os teus clientes. Foco onde faz sentido para o teu negócio, em vez de estar em todas ao mesmo tempo.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Tenho de aparecer ou gravar vídeos?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Não é obrigatório. Trabalho com o que tiveres (fotos, vídeos do dia a dia) e crio conteúdo à volta disso. Para Reels, oriento-te se quiseres gravar tu mesmo.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Quantos posts por mês?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Depende do plano — definimos um volume controlado à cabeça, para garantir qualidade e não saturar nem o teu feed nem o teu tempo.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"As redes vão fazer o meu negócio explodir?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Sinceramente, não sozinhas. As redes são um complemento — o motor do crescimento é o teu site e o SEO. O que fazem é manter-te presente, credível e na memória de quem te segue.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Posso pedir só um pack pontual?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Sim. Tens o Pack de Posts (avulso) e o Pack Vídeo Vertical (pagamento único), sem teres de assinar uma avença mensal.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Como começo?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Pedes um orçamento no formulário (2 minutos). Respondo em menos de 2 horas, sem compromisso.\"}}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-[820px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4\">FAQ</p><h2 id=\"faq\" class=\"text-white\">Perguntas frequentes sobre redes sociais</h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-accent/30 bg-bg-card\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-0\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-0\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white\">Em que redes trabalham?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-0\"></span></span></button></h3><div id=\"faq-a-0\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"faq-q-0\" class=\"overflow-hidden\" style=\"height:auto;opacity:1\"><p class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Instagram, Facebook e TikTok — conforme onde estão os teus clientes. Foco onde faz sentido para o teu negócio, em vez de estar em todas ao mesmo tempo.</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-1\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">Tenho de aparecer ou gravar vídeos?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-2\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-2\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">Quantos posts por mês?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-3\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">As redes vão fazer o meu negócio explodir?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-4\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-4\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">Posso pedir só um pack pontual?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n              border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-5\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white/85\">Como começo?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-100\"></span></span></button></h3></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-bg to-[#08090b] border-t border-white/10 py-28 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"cta\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bottom-0 w-[760px] h-[420px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 100%, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.20), transparent 70%)\"></div><div class=\"relative max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-5\">O próximo passo</p><h2 id=\"cta\" class=\"text-white\">Pronto para redes que te representam — sem o trabalho?</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto\">Conta-me onde queres estar. Trato do resto. Respondo pessoalmente em menos de 2 horas, sem compromisso.</p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-5\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body \" href=\"/contacto?servico=Social%20Media\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Quero as minhas redes ativas</span></a><a class=\"text-sm text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"mailto:info@elementgroup.pt\">ou escreve-me para <span class=\"text-white/90 underline underline-offset-4\">info@elementgroup.pt</span></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-20 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"outros-servicos\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-3\">Explora mais</p><h2 id=\"outros-servicos\" class=\"text-white\">Outros serviços</h2></div><div class=\"mt-10 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><a style=\"--accent-rgb:127 168 217\" class=\"group relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-bg-card p-6 h-full transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-[rgb(var(--accent-rgb)/0.5)]\" href=\"/servicos/web\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-70 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(120% 100% at 85% 0%, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16), transparent 58%)\"></span><span class=\"relative flex